1
00:01:56,820 --> 00:02:02,820
=The Unexpected Marriage=

2
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:07,660
=Episode 9=

3
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:28,940
I, Liu Changsheng,

4
00:02:29,420 --> 00:02:31,060
am willing to go to Great Tang.

5
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:38,620
I'm willing to make the alliance

6
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:39,780
with Great Tang

7
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:41,020
and dedicate my whole life

8
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,300
to protect Fuyu.

9
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:43,180
Good.

10
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,340
You're indeed from the royal family.

11
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,420
Rise.

12
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:49,180
With courage,

13
00:02:49,180 --> 00:02:50,860
ambitious and aspiration.

14
00:02:50,860 --> 00:02:52,220
I will now draft a decree.

15
00:02:52,940 --> 00:02:53,780
Gao An.

16
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:54,860
Yes.

17
00:02:56,020 --> 00:02:56,900
Mr. Envoy.

18
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:58,380
What do you think?

19
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:00,100
It's my pleasure.

20
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:01,740
I will not disappoint Her Highness.

21
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:04,580
Your Majesty.

22
00:03:04,620 --> 00:03:06,100
I have another request.

23
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:06,940
Say it.

24
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:08,500
I will definitely grant it.

25
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:09,860
Please allow me

26
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:11,500
to ask you a favor.

27
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:13,940
I hope Your Majesty will give me

28
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,580
thirty Muyan trees

29
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,020
and send them to Great Tang too.

30
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:18,700
I know

31
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:19,660
Muyan tree

32
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:21,220
is the core of Fuyu's salt business.

33
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:23,220
Since the founding of the country,
it's never been given away.

34
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:25,620
But if we can present thirty Muyan trees
as a gift,

35
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:27,260
it'll certainly express

36
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:28,260
our determination

37
00:03:28,260 --> 00:03:29,540
to get along amicably with Great Tang.

38
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:31,820
Plus my negotiation,

39
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:33,220
preferably we can establish

40
00:03:33,220 --> 00:03:34,300
trade relations with Great Tang.

41
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:36,300
It must be a good thing
for the country and the people.

42
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,460
Granted.

43
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:39,460
Your Highness is generous.

44
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,140
Please rest assured, Your Majesty.

45
00:03:41,340 --> 00:03:43,660
I will never let Her Highness
suffer any injustice.

46
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:49,020
Your Majesty.

47
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,420
I would like to ask for your permission

48
00:03:50,940 --> 00:03:52,860
for me to go to Great Tang together

49
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:53,820
as the envoy.

50
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:57,300
You want to be an envoy?

51
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:58,140
Yes.

52
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:04,660
Absolutely not.

53
00:04:05,140 --> 00:04:06,100
I disagree.

54
00:04:11,660 --> 00:04:12,500
Zilv.

55
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:14,660
Father.

56
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:16,460
I've decided to go.

57
00:04:16,740 --> 00:04:17,580
You...

58
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,420
There's only one man
in every generation of our family.

59
00:04:23,020 --> 00:04:23,980
You are

60
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:24,980
the only son we have.

61
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,420
Do you know

62
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:28,100
the trip to Great Tang

63
00:04:28,580 --> 00:04:30,220
will be dangerous,

64
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:31,380
and you may not

65
00:04:31,380 --> 00:04:32,660
come back alive?

66
00:04:33,020 --> 00:04:33,980
But you...

67
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:41,900
Father, have some tea.

68
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:43,140
I don't want to.

69
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:45,220
Therefore,

70
00:04:45,980 --> 00:04:47,500
I should stay by her side.

71
00:04:47,740 --> 00:04:48,860
You fool!

72
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,980
Did you read the books

73
00:04:51,460 --> 00:04:53,060
in vain?

74
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:55,060
Have you forgotten about

75
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,500
filial piety?

76
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:12,860
I'm unfilial.

77
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,420
His Majesty has

78
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:17,540
granted my wish.

79
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:19,460
You...

80
00:05:19,660 --> 00:05:20,980
You ungrateful child.

81
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:22,740
You actually used His Majesty to pressure me.

82
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,340
Father.

83
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:25,380
Father.

84
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:26,740
How rebellious!

85
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:28,220
How rebellious!

86
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:31,540
How could I have such an unfilial son like you?

87
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:34,940
Do you know how to write
the words "filial piety"?

88
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:36,980
Write it a thousand times!

89
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:51,500
(Self-discipline and Social Commitment)
Here's the imperial decree.

90
00:05:58,020 --> 00:06:00,380
Liu Changsheng, receive it.

91
00:06:01,940 --> 00:06:02,780
His Majesty said

92
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:04,620
Your Royal Highnesses don't have to kneel.

93
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:05,580
Thank you.

94
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:06,660
I'm here.

95
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,500
Pursuant to Heaven's will,

96
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,060
hereby orders,

97
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:11,700
Princess Changsheng

98
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:13,260
is born talented

99
00:06:13,260 --> 00:06:14,980
and intelligent.

100
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:16,860
Go to Great Tang

101
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:19,260
in favor of closer relations.

102
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:21,820
Princess Changsheng, please accept the decree.

103
00:06:30,940 --> 00:06:34,820
This is the gift list drafted by His Majesty.

104
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:39,260
Reward Princess Changsheng

105
00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:41,140
a pair of jade pots,

106
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,260
- a box of red agate,
- What is all this?

107
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:44,180
So stingy.

108
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:46,020
the paintings of The Beautiful Lady Yu,

109
00:06:46,460 --> 00:06:48,380
Bamboo Flowers,

110
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:50,620
Auspicious Crane.

111
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:51,460
Mr. Gao.

112
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:54,580
Stop reading them one by one.

113
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:55,900
Yes.

114
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:58,700
Anyway, I've finished reading.

115
00:06:58,700 --> 00:06:59,940
(A pair of white jade,
A pair of Jade Ruyi)

116
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:07,460
Oh, and there are thirty Muyan saplings.

117
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:08,980
We've gotten them prepared.

118
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,780
Please rest assured, Your Highness.

119
00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:12,740
Your Royal Highness.

120
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:14,700
His Majesty also said

121
00:07:14,700 --> 00:07:17,620
the farewell banquet should be hosted by you.

122
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,060
Don't worry about the rules.

123
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:20,740
Just organize it as you please.

124
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,420
I lost my daughter for nothing.

125
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:26,100
He's just so stingy.

126
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:28,420
You brother is really...

127
00:07:29,620 --> 00:07:30,540
That's how it is.

128
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:31,980
If you cough, he's still stingy.

129
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:42,180
I'm sorry, my daughter.

130
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,780
(Gorgeous Vernal Scenery)

131
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,100
Yi'an, why haven't you slept yet?

132
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:17,780
Your Highness is awake too.

133
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:21,540
I'm finally getting married.

134
00:08:21,940 --> 00:08:23,460
I'm so happy that I couldn't sleep.

135
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:27,340
Really?

136
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:31,180
I've spoken my heart many times,

137
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:32,620
but you didn't listen,

138
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:33,780
didn't answer

139
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:34,780
and didn't allow.

140
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:37,020
Now you ask me whether it's true.

141
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:46,620
Whether it's sincere or false,

142
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:48,140
it's become a fact.

143
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:50,220
More talk is useless.

144
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:51,740
Let's just drink tea.

145
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:02,900
I heard Xiao Zilv

146
00:09:03,220 --> 00:09:04,740
is punished by Mr. Xiao

147
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:06,700
to write "filial piety" a thousand times

148
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:08,060
in the courtyard.

149
00:09:21,460 --> 00:09:22,740
It's not cold when it snows,

150
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:24,100
but it's cold when snow melts.

151
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:27,260
Hopefully after the snow stops,

152
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:30,100
his determination to follow me to Great Tang

153
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,540
can also cool down.

154
00:09:58,100 --> 00:10:03,270
♪Sitting alone in the west window,
quietly watching the snow♪

155
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:11,180
♪Silently falling and piling up♪

156
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:15,660
(Filial Piety)

157
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:23,480
♪And withered at night♪

158
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:24,840
(Filial Piety)

159
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:30,660
♪Facing the freezing north wind♪

160
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:37,840
♪Looking at you, it's hard to say goodbye♪

161
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:42,670
♪I fear the heat will fade away in an instant♪

162
00:10:42,940 --> 00:10:43,780
- Zilv.
- Mother.

163
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:44,940
Mother.

164
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,780
If you take one step forward,

165
00:10:48,780 --> 00:10:50,940
I will die in front of you.

166
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:52,260
Zilv, go!

167
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,820
Meet His Majesty

168
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,700
and marry Changsheng.

169
00:10:57,180 --> 00:10:58,620
How rebellious!

170
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:00,300
How rebellious!

171
00:11:00,820 --> 00:11:02,940
Do you know how to write
the words "filial piety"?

172
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:04,900
Write it a thousand times!

173
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:10,450
♪Let the yearning for you♪

174
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:14,320
♪Run wild♪

175
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:20,540
♪How can a lonely lamp comfort me♪

176
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:29,860
(Filial Piety)

177
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:47,700
(Self-discipline and Social Commitment)

178
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:49,940
Everyone, enjoy the meal.

179
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:54,980
Sit down. Sit down.

180
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:56,020
Sit, sit down.

181
00:11:56,650 --> 00:11:57,490
Come, please.

182
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:04,420
Congratulations,

183
00:12:04,420 --> 00:12:05,740
Your Royal Highness.

184
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:07,540
Today is a big day for you.

185
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:09,060
We'll toast you, Your Royal Highness.

186
00:12:09,300 --> 00:12:10,220
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

187
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:17,260
Your Royal Highness.

188
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:19,780
Princess Changsheng is an excellent woman.

189
00:12:20,140 --> 00:12:22,660
You've taught her well.

190
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:25,060
Princess Changsheng is carrying

191
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:27,420
the hope and future of our Fuyu people.

192
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:28,580
Prince Changle's Mansion

193
00:12:28,820 --> 00:12:30,060
has such an honor.

194
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:30,900
Right.

195
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:32,820
Excellent?

196
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:36,540
Honor?

197
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:40,780
I've raised my daughter

198
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:43,940
for over ten years.

199
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:46,180
I don't want her to be excellent

200
00:12:46,620 --> 00:12:48,940
or bring honor to the family.

201
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:50,780
I just want her to be happy.

202
00:12:59,580 --> 00:13:01,100
I didn't sleep for three days and nights

203
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:03,220
to write this play,

204
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:04,540
"Princess Marrying Far Away".

205
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:06,660
Although there are many twists and turns,

206
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:08,780
it's still a happy ending.

207
00:13:09,060 --> 00:13:10,460
Your Highness, today

208
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:11,940
I meet you

209
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:13,100
in my true identity.

210
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:14,980
In the future, you and I

211
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:16,340
must be together forever.

212
00:13:16,340 --> 00:13:17,780
(Did she see something?)

213
00:13:17,980 --> 00:13:19,260
What do you think?

214
00:13:19,260 --> 00:13:20,980
You lied to me.

215
00:13:21,740 --> 00:13:22,580
It's coming.

216
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:23,620
The best part is coming.

217
00:13:23,620 --> 00:13:25,540
How could you lie to me?

218
00:13:26,100 --> 00:13:27,260
I'm not afraid

219
00:13:27,260 --> 00:13:29,140
of leaving home

220
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:31,020
and having a long journey.

221
00:13:31,020 --> 00:13:32,940
I believed in you.

222
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:33,780
But

223
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:36,420
how dare you lie to me?

224
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:40,900
Princess.

225
00:13:40,900 --> 00:13:42,540
Princess!

226
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:50,460
This play is so...

227
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:52,140
So unlucky.

228
00:13:52,820 --> 00:13:53,660
Guangde.

229
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:55,620
I haven't left Fuyu

230
00:13:55,620 --> 00:13:56,980
and you already killed me.

231
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:02,740
You misunderstood the meaning of this play.

232
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:04,220
My idea is too nice

233
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,530
and my literary attainments are too high.

234
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:06,460
But that's okay.

235
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:07,820
I gave them a happy ending.

236
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,660
Why didn't Xiao Zilv come?

237
00:14:25,300 --> 00:14:27,020
Zilv knelt in the snow for a whole night

238
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:28,540
and hurt his knees.

239
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:30,500
He already had an old injury on his leg.

240
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:31,980
I'm afraid he can't come today.

241
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:35,460
Father saw Zilv was determined to leave,

242
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:36,700
after beating,

243
00:14:36,700 --> 00:14:37,540
scolding

244
00:14:37,700 --> 00:14:38,540
and punishing him,

245
00:14:39,100 --> 00:14:40,260
he finally agreed.

246
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:42,060
Changsheng.

247
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:43,140
You must take care

248
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:45,260
in the future.

249
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:56,020
Zilv.

250
00:14:59,260 --> 00:15:00,860
It's Her Highness's banquet.

251
00:15:01,060 --> 00:15:02,180
As the envoy,

252
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:03,020
of course I should come.

253
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:09,700
Mr. Xiao has a serious leg problem.

254
00:15:09,940 --> 00:15:11,220
It's better to go back home and rest.

255
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:13,700
Otherwise, it'll be hard to follow Her Highness

256
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:14,860
to Great Tang.

257
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:16,740
Please rest assured, Mr. Envoy.

258
00:15:17,060 --> 00:15:18,780
For the safety of Changsheng,

259
00:15:18,780 --> 00:15:19,820
I will not delay the trip

260
00:15:20,020 --> 00:15:20,940
and drag her down.

261
00:15:21,540 --> 00:15:22,380
Don't worry, Changsheng.

262
00:15:22,820 --> 00:15:23,660
I'm fine.

263
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:24,780
That's good.

264
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:37,660
Don't move.

265
00:15:37,660 --> 00:15:38,540
Let me do it.

266
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:41,300
I'll do it.

267
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,220
Farewell, Your Royal Highness.

268
00:16:02,220 --> 00:16:03,380
Goodbye.

269
00:16:03,380 --> 00:16:04,220
Farewell.

270
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:05,980
- Your Royal Highness, I'm leaving now.
- Goodbye.

271
00:16:06,190 --> 00:16:07,540
- Take care, Your Royal Highness.
- Take care.

272
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:08,380
Goodbye.

273
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:10,420
Goodbye.

274
00:16:10,420 --> 00:16:11,260
Dad.

275
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:13,100
Changsheng.

276
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:15,300
- Changsheng.
- He's drunk.

277
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:17,260
Changsheng.

278
00:16:17,260 --> 00:16:19,100
Mom, help Dad go back and have a rest.

279
00:16:19,460 --> 00:16:20,300
Changsheng.

280
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:21,700
Let's go back.

281
00:16:21,700 --> 00:16:23,740
I can't bear to leave you.

282
00:16:23,740 --> 00:16:25,100
Changsheng.

283
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:31,580
Changsheng.

284
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:38,060
Changsheng, we're leaving.

285
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:40,340
(Self-discipline and Social Commitment)

286
00:16:40,340 --> 00:16:41,180
Xiao Zilv.

287
00:16:42,220 --> 00:16:43,420
I have something to tell you.

288
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:45,860
If you want me to elope with you now,

289
00:16:45,860 --> 00:16:46,780
is it too late?

290
00:16:51,740 --> 00:16:53,460
I lost my handkerchief.

291
00:16:53,740 --> 00:16:55,180
Guangde, come with me to look for it.

292
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:56,860
If you lose it, just buy a new one.

293
00:16:56,860 --> 00:16:58,340
Please go with me to look for it.

294
00:16:58,340 --> 00:16:59,260
You can go with me too.

295
00:16:59,260 --> 00:17:00,100
Changsheng.

296
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:21,580
Tomorrow I will go and ask His Majesty

297
00:17:21,820 --> 00:17:22,940
to let you stay.

298
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:25,060
Liu Changsheng.

299
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:26,780
I'm going to Great Tang to study medicine

300
00:17:26,780 --> 00:17:27,700
and open my eyes.

301
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:29,680
You're marrying Prince Qin.

302
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:30,940
But don't ruin my future.

303
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:31,780
Xiao Zilv.

304
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:33,820
I'm not going to Great Tang for fun.

305
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:34,940
I'm not playing either.

306
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,540
I'm going to study.

307
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:37,940
You don't know how happy my father is

308
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,060
