309
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,380
He thinks I'm an honor to the family.

310
00:17:40,780 --> 00:17:42,980
Maybe I can even marry a princess.

311
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:45,140
Anyway, I don't mind your business,

312
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:46,070
and you don't mind mine either.

313
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:47,060
Don't ruin my plan.

314
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:55,220
Your Highness.

315
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:57,020
Yi'an.

316
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:58,700
In my opinion,

317
00:17:59,060 --> 00:17:59,900
being the envoy

318
00:18:00,220 --> 00:18:01,860
is not Mr. Xiao's

319
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:03,220
only idea.

320
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:04,780
Whatever you think,

321
00:18:05,180 --> 00:18:06,660
and whatever he's thinking,

322
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:08,860
I will still go

323
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:11,380
for the peace-making marriage.

324
00:18:11,620 --> 00:18:12,700
Mr. Envoy.

325
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:13,900
What else is there to worry about?

326
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:16,340
I clearly know

327
00:18:16,860 --> 00:18:17,740
my responsibilities.

328
00:18:18,380 --> 00:18:20,740
I'll be devoted to Prince Qin of Great Tang.

329
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:26,380
As for the others...

330
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:43,420
Let's toast Changsheng.

331
00:18:52,460 --> 00:18:53,780
There is none left.

332
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:56,020
Give me.

333
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:59,780
During the day, when General Zhao was here,

334
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:01,300
