335
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:04,540
Why did you become an alcoholic now?

336
00:19:04,540 --> 00:19:06,500
He usually doesn't let me drink.

337
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:08,660
And you listen to him?

338
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:10,860
The lawless Liu Guangde

339
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:12,580
finally met her nemesis.

340
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:15,100
I'm more impressed

341
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:16,820
with Zhao Huaibi now.

342
00:19:16,820 --> 00:19:18,020
Well,

343
00:19:18,020 --> 00:19:20,180
