344
00:19:20,820 --> 00:19:22,500
I'm getting married.

345
00:19:23,020 --> 00:19:24,780
Xiao Jin is also going to Wu.

346
00:19:25,260 --> 00:19:26,820
You're going to Great Tang.

347
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:29,180
Later,

348
00:19:29,180 --> 00:19:31,020
I'm afraid we can't

349
00:19:31,020 --> 00:19:32,660
get together

350
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:34,820
