352
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:38,660
I'll drink more.

353
00:19:39,540 --> 00:19:40,860
I thought

354
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:43,100
even if I marry into the Xie family,

355
00:19:44,020 --> 00:19:45,660
they're an open-minded family,

356
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:47,980
and I can still meet you once a year.

357
00:19:48,820 --> 00:19:49,660
Now

358
00:19:50,220 --> 00:19:51,740
you're going to Great Tang.

359
00:19:52,020 --> 00:19:53,420
It's in a far distance.

360
00:19:53,940 --> 00:19:54,860
Maybe

361
00:19:56,300 --> 00:19:58,500
I'll never see you again.

362
00:20:02,060 --> 00:20:03,100
Tell me,

363
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:04,580
