364
00:20:04,820 --> 00:20:06,060
always have to make sacrifices?

365
00:20:06,620 --> 00:20:07,580
Or what?

366
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:10,580
Men can do this, too.

367
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:11,860
I think it makes sense.

368
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:13,460
Right?

369
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:14,740
In the future,

370
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:17,460
I will marry a man from another country.

371
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:21,980
Forget it.

372
00:20:21,980 --> 00:20:23,220
I'm getting married.

373
00:20:25,020 --> 00:20:27,020
