374
00:20:28,860 --> 00:20:29,700
Oh,

375
00:20:29,860 --> 00:20:30,700
Changsheng.

376
00:20:30,860 --> 00:20:32,580
Close your eyes first.

377
00:20:32,580 --> 00:20:33,740
I'll give you something.

378
00:20:35,540 --> 00:20:36,660
