384
00:20:57,860 --> 00:20:59,060
This thing...

385
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:02,940
I won't tell you.

386
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:03,780
Anyway,

387
00:21:04,180 --> 00:21:06,060
