394
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:30,340
Don't be mad at them.

395
00:21:30,540 --> 00:21:31,420
I've bothered you for days.

396
00:21:31,820 --> 00:21:32,940
Now the mission is complete,

397
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:34,020
I should go.

398
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,660
I will be staying at posthouse near here.

399
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:37,940
If you have something,

400
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:39,180
come find me.

401
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:40,820
At this point,

402
00:21:40,820 --> 00:21:42,180
