403
00:21:44,460 --> 00:21:45,700
Just set off with peace of mind.

404
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:18,420
You two

405
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:19,500
take this box to the room.

406
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,340
- Yes.
- Yes.

407
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:26,020
Sir.

408
00:22:28,580 --> 00:22:29,420
Sir.

409
00:22:29,540 --> 00:22:31,540
I just caught a big fish in the river.

410
00:22:31,900 --> 00:22:33,540
Should we steam or braise it?

411
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:35,100
Or we can try sashimi.

412
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:36,500
Changsheng.

413
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:37,820
Changsheng is here?

414
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:38,980
Princess Changsheng is here?

415
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:40,500
Where?

416
00:22:40,820 --> 00:22:41,700
Ask her to eat with us.

417
00:22:45,660 --> 00:22:46,500
I don't see her.

418
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:52,820
Princess Changsheng

419
00:22:52,820 --> 00:22:53,980
