424
00:23:02,940 --> 00:23:03,780
This fish is good.

425
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:05,780
It's my fish.

426
00:23:20,260 --> 00:23:21,100
Sir.

427
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,140
The bodyguard reported

428
00:23:22,340 --> 00:23:24,620
