will follow you back to Great Tang,

429
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:26,620
and the rest stay in Fuyu.

430
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:28,860
Is this arrangement appropriate?

431
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:32,700
Sir.

432
00:23:35,060 --> 00:23:35,940
After Changsheng

433
00:23:37,500 --> 00:23:39,300
marries into Great Tang

434
00:23:39,300 --> 00:23:40,620
and learns about my identity,

435
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,340
