436
00:23:42,620 --> 00:23:44,220
A girl like Princess Changsheng

437
00:23:44,220 --> 00:23:45,220
who's talented

438
00:23:45,220 --> 00:23:47,100
and has her own ideas

439
00:23:47,100 --> 00:23:48,860
can't accept being deceived by others.

440
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:51,300
If she finds herself being cheated,

441
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:52,180
and the one who cheated her

442
00:23:52,180 --> 00:23:53,580
is someone close to her,

443
00:23:54,380 --> 00:23:56,460
I guess she will react intensely.

444
00:23:56,740 --> 00:23:57,580
Maybe

445
00:23:57,940 --> 00:23:59,500
she'll use extreme means

446
00:23:59,500 --> 00:24:00,860
to make her stand.

447
00:24:02,820 --> 00:24:04,820
You lied to me!

448
00:24:08,740 --> 00:24:10,020
But even so,

449
00:24:10,020 --> 00:24:11,180
you don't have to worry.

450
00:24:11,500 --> 00:24:13,380
With the excuse

451
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,220
of Princess Changsheng

452
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:15,900
turning against Prince Qin,

453
00:24:15,900 --> 00:24:17,060
you can delcare war on Fuyu.

454
00:24:17,060 --> 00:24:18,700
It's righteous and reasonable.

455
00:24:19,220 --> 00:24:22,420
But it's a pity that Princess Changsheng...

456
00:24:26,900 --> 00:24:27,740
Actually,

457
00:24:28,340 --> 00:24:29,380
according to my observation

458
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:31,500
of Princess Changsheng in recent days,

459
00:24:31,860 --> 00:24:32,700
Her Highness

460
00:24:32,820 --> 00:24:34,220
is not

461
00:24:34,220 --> 00:24:35,420
an unreasonable person.

462
00:24:36,020 --> 00:24:38,380
Even if she knows your identity,

463
00:24:39,060 --> 00:24:41,420
I guess she won't mind.

464
00:24:42,100 --> 00:24:43,780
Do you want to reveal your true identity

465
00:24:44,060 --> 00:24:45,100
to Her Highness?

466
00:24:46,340 --> 00:24:47,540
Bring me a pen and ink.

467
00:25:09,980 --> 00:25:11,900
(Yi'an)

468
00:25:21,660 --> 00:25:22,580
Give this to Changsheng.

469
00:25:23,580 --> 00:25:24,390
Okay.

470
00:25:24,390 --> 00:25:25,420
Let the bodyguard come to see me.

471
00:25:25,420 --> 00:25:26,260
Yes.

472
00:25:26,860 --> 00:25:27,700
Let's go.

473
00:25:31,820 --> 00:25:37,860
(Fengqing Guesthouse)

474
00:25:43,420 --> 00:25:44,260
What?

475
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:48,420
