I've been lazy recently?

476
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:49,860
Otherwise, why does he treat me like this?

477
00:25:52,260 --> 00:25:53,700
He just thinks you are stupid.

478
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:55,700
Why am I stupid?

479
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:57,420
You've been with him for so long.

480
00:25:58,700 --> 00:25:59,540
You idiot.

481
00:25:59,780 --> 00:26:01,460
You still don't know what he's thinking.

482
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:04,300
(Fengqing Guesthouse)

483
00:26:04,300 --> 00:26:06,220
Do you know there is a saying called

484
00:26:06,220 --> 00:26:09,460
a hero is hard to resist a beauty?

485
00:26:17,540 --> 00:26:19,620
(Gorgeous Vernal Scenery)

486
00:26:22,220 --> 00:26:24,380
Hibiscus needs to loosen the soil
three times a day.

487
00:26:25,500 --> 00:26:26,380
When watering it,

488
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:28,020
remember to avoid standing water.

489
00:26:28,300 --> 00:26:29,140
Yes.

490
00:26:34,260 --> 00:26:35,100
By the way,

491
00:26:35,460 --> 00:26:37,020
pay special attention on moisture.

492
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,620
- Remember to clean up
- Yes.

493
00:26:38,620 --> 00:26:39,560
the water in the basin in time.

494
00:26:39,860 --> 00:26:40,700
OK.

495
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:49,460
It's almost the season
for begonia flowers to bloom.

496
00:26:57,420 --> 00:26:58,740
Mother likes begonia the most.

497
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:01,180
Remember to take the begonia flowers

498
00:27:01,180 --> 00:27:02,380
outside to bathe in the sun.

499
00:27:03,180 --> 00:27:04,260
The better the sunshine,

500
00:27:04,260 --> 00:27:05,300
the better the flowers bloom.

501
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:06,340
Yes.

502
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:10,860
Your Highness.

503
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:12,700
What's wrong?

504
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:13,820
Your Highness.

505
00:27:13,900 --> 00:27:15,380
Young Master asked me to give you this.

506
00:27:20,740 --> 00:27:22,740
Even though the grass withers,

507
00:27:23,380 --> 00:27:25,300
the fallen flowers will meet again elsewhere.

508
00:27:26,060 --> 00:27:27,700
(Yi'an)
After parting ways with old friends,

509
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:30,460
I only wish for you to know me.

510
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:31,820
I'm waiting for you.

511
00:27:32,260 --> 00:27:33,420
Is it that

512
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:35,300
he can't let go of me

513
00:27:35,740 --> 00:27:36,780
and is reluctant to leave me,

514
00:27:37,500 --> 00:27:38,820
so he doesn't want to go back to Great Tang?

515
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:42,620
Where is Yi'an now?

516
00:27:42,620 --> 00:27:43,540
Still in the posthouse.

517
00:27:45,180 --> 00:27:46,020
(It's over.)

518
00:27:46,340 --> 00:27:47,620
(My guess was correct.)

519
00:27:48,060 --> 00:27:48,900
(So)

520
00:27:49,060 --> 00:27:50,420
(is he waiting for my reply)

521
00:27:50,940 --> 00:27:52,820
(and will not leave until I come?)

522
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:55,780
Tell Yi'an for me

523
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:57,540
that I received the letter.

524
00:27:58,140 --> 00:27:59,220
Let me think about it.

525
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:00,820
She didn't say anything else?

526
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:02,180
After Princess Changsheng

527
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:03,260
received this letter,

528
00:28:03,260 --> 00:28:04,740
I've told you

529
00:28:04,740 --> 00:28:05,940
every expression she made

530
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:07,740
and every word she said.

531
00:28:08,740 --> 00:28:09,580
Presumably,

532
00:28:10,220 --> 00:28:11,500
she must understand what I mean.

533
00:28:12,220 --> 00:28:13,300
Your Highness.

534
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:14,500
You keep walking around.

535
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:16,300
I've started to see double.

536
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:17,820
I think

537
00:28:17,820 --> 00:28:19,180
you have to calm down.

538
00:28:19,700 --> 00:28:21,540
I shouldn't have said these words.

539
00:28:21,540 --> 00:28:23,140
But for your lifelong happiness,

540
00:28:23,140 --> 00:28:24,020
I must say.

541
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:25,540
Throughout our life,

542
00:28:25,540 --> 00:28:26,980
it's extremely hard to meet

543
00:28:26,980 --> 00:28:27,940
someone who truly loves you

544
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:29,140
and understands you,

545
00:28:29,140 --> 00:28:30,180
and spend the rest of life

546
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:31,660
with him.

547
00:28:31,660 --> 00:28:33,740
Marriage is a big deal.

548
00:28:34,140 --> 00:28:36,020
You are going for the peace-making marriage.

549
00:28:36,020 --> 00:28:37,660
You're the future wife of Prince Qin.

550
00:28:37,860 --> 00:28:39,180
If you elope with

551
00:28:39,180 --> 00:28:41,220
