556
00:28:46,700 --> 00:28:47,540
Your Highness.

557
00:28:47,540 --> 00:28:48,740
You should be careful.

558
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:49,740
At this critical moment,

559
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:50,820
