566
00:29:05,100 --> 00:29:06,380
These are two different things.

567
00:29:07,060 --> 00:29:07,900
Shenxing.

568
00:29:08,340 --> 00:29:10,500
This feeling is meant to become recollection.

569
00:29:11,500 --> 00:29:12,540
What is the next sentence?

570
00:29:13,020 --> 00:29:16,100
This feeling is meant...

571
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:22,100
But at the time we experience,
