572
00:29:23,020 --> 00:29:23,980
So

573
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:26,260
I must marry into Great Tang.

574
00:29:28,260 --> 00:29:29,380
There's no fate

575
00:29:30,260 --> 00:29:31,580
between him and I.

576
00:29:35,340 --> 00:29:36,740
But Jinyan was right.

577
00:29:38,780 --> 00:29:40,020
Yi'an treats me sincerely.

578
00:29:41,100 --> 00:29:41,980
Anyway,

579
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:43,620
I should go see him

