605
00:31:15,460 --> 00:31:16,860
There's still a long way to go.

606
00:31:19,740 --> 00:31:21,460
You have to let go of your obsession

607
00:31:22,180 --> 00:31:24,740
- then we can be...
- Your Highness.

608
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:27,820
Youmou?

609
00:31:31,620 --> 00:31:32,500
Your Highness.

610
00:31:32,700 --> 00:31:33,540
Spare the formalities.

611
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,540
Who is this?

612
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:43,660
