615
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:12,060
Changsheng.

616
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:13,060
Sir.

617
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:17,300
You guys leave us first.

618
00:32:17,660 --> 00:32:18,500
Let's go.

619
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:25,220
Sir.

620
00:32:25,420 --> 00:32:26,260
What?

621
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:27,980
Do we need to adjust

622
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:28,820
the return date?

623
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,260
No.

624
00:32:30,660 --> 00:32:32,300
We'll depart tomorrow as planned.

625
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:35,300
Go back.

626
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:39,220
Aren't you not leaving?

627
00:32:39,620 --> 00:32:40,660
Who said I'm not leaving?

628
00:32:41,020 --> 00:32:42,460
You said in the letter

629
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:44,980
that you would wait for me.

630
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:46,140
I will always wait for you.

631
00:32:46,740 --> 00:32:48,100
But I'll wait for you in Great Tang.

632
00:32:50,860 --> 00:32:52,540
Then why did you write the letter?

633
00:32:52,740 --> 00:32:54,260
You made a mistake.

634
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:56,780
I don't mean anything else.

635
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:59,460
Just don't get me wrong.

636
00:33:01,860 --> 00:33:03,700
(It was a big joke.)

637
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:06,060
Interesting.

638
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:08,380
- I am leaving.
- Okay.

639
00:33:10,460 --> 00:33:11,300
Changsheng.

640
00:33:11,380 --> 00:33:12,260
I'll walk you out.

641
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:13,460
No, thanks.

642
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:15,340
I'll walk you out.

643
00:33:27,740 --> 00:33:29,730
Why do I feel Young Master is very happy?

644
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:32,940
I think

645
00:33:33,780 --> 00:33:35,460
it's too early to be happy.

646
00:33:35,580 --> 00:33:38,910
(Prince Changle's Mansion)

647
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:46,820
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

648
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:06,500
Aren't you not leaving?

649
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,100
Who said I'm not leaving?

650
00:34:08,100 --> 00:34:09,380
You said you would wait for me.

651
00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:10,460
I will always wait for you.

652
00:34:11,140 --> 00:34:12,460
But I'll wait for you in Great Tang.

653
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:31,940
Changsheng.

654
00:34:32,660 --> 00:34:33,500
Mother.

655
00:34:33,940 --> 00:34:35,380
I knitted some colorful yarn

656
00:34:35,620 --> 00:34:37,420
and put it in your travel box.

657
00:34:38,060 --> 00:34:39,100
This colorful yarn

658
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:41,140
is only available in Fuyu.

659
00:34:42,500 --> 00:34:44,380
I wanted to make a wedding dress for you

660
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,540
when you get married.

661
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:48,140
Now you are marrying to Great Tang.

662
00:34:49,220 --> 00:34:51,620
You'll wear Great Tang's dress
on your wedding day.

663
00:34:51,900 --> 00:34:53,180
I think it's no longer useful.

664
00:34:55,900 --> 00:34:58,060
Mother, don't be sad.

665
00:34:58,620 --> 00:35:00,140
I'm doing fine.

666
00:35:00,540 --> 00:35:01,820
I can finally get married.

667
00:35:02,380 --> 00:35:03,740
I heard from Yi'an

668
00:35:03,740 --> 00:35:04,900
that Prince Qin is a good person.

669
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:06,420
He has a dignified appearance

670
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:07,660
and easygoing personality.

671
00:35:08,020 --> 00:35:09,620
How can you believe his words?

672
00:35:10,260 --> 00:35:11,620
He is Prince Qin's confidant.

673
00:35:12,140 --> 00:35:13,220
I've heard it all.

674
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:15,740
Prince Qin is cruel and violent.

675
00:35:17,300 --> 00:35:18,140
That's...

676
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:21,980
That's rumors made up
by people who are jealous of him.

677
00:35:23,020 --> 00:35:24,780
Yi'an's words are trustworthy.

678
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:27,300
Mother.

679
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:28,900
Don't worry.

680
00:35:31,380 --> 00:35:32,260
Everything

681
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:35,420
