684
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,280
Take care.

685
00:35:45,610 --> 00:35:47,040
Your Highness, take care.

686
00:35:47,570 --> 00:35:49,020
This is quite a scene.

687
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:10,220
Your Highness, you're bored.

688
00:36:10,220 --> 00:36:11,700
Let's take a look at the dowry

689
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:12,580
to kill the time.

690
00:36:12,580 --> 00:36:13,740
- Okay.
- Jinyan.

691
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:16,020
Your Highness, be careful about what you do.

692
00:36:16,290 --> 00:36:18,260
Before leaving, His Royal Highness
repeatedly reminded us

693
00:36:18,260 --> 00:36:20,780
the treasures inside are all priceless.

694
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:22,620
We should watch it carefully.

695
00:36:22,620 --> 00:36:24,460
And he also said...

696
00:36:24,730 --> 00:36:25,580
Said what?

697
00:36:25,580 --> 00:36:26,980
I need to keep an eye on you.

698
00:36:26,980 --> 00:36:28,580
Don't open the box in advance.

699
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:29,820
It's for me.

700
00:36:30,060 --> 00:36:31,220
Why can't I open it?

701
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:32,420
I want to see it.

702
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,340
Then go ahead.

703
00:36:36,140 --> 00:36:37,060
That's what you said.

704
00:36:43,820 --> 00:36:45,540
(Pregnant Pill)

705
00:36:46,020 --> 00:36:47,660
Pregnant Pill.

706
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:50,660
Weird.

707
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:54,940
Nourishment Pills.

708
00:36:55,900 --> 00:36:57,020
Absurd.

709
00:37:00,820 --> 00:37:03,300
I thought Dad gave me some rare treasure.

710
00:37:03,820 --> 00:37:06,140
Am I going to marry or to die?

711
00:37:07,340 --> 00:37:08,300
So many medicines.

712
00:37:08,620 --> 00:37:09,980
I will get sick from eating these.

713
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:12,060
Your Highness, watch your words.

714
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:13,460
No disease.

715
00:37:14,220 --> 00:37:15,220
But I'll get sick from this.

716
00:37:15,220 --> 00:37:16,860
Your Highness, watch your actions.

717
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:18,860
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

718
00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:21,660
But we are not so sure.

719
00:37:21,660 --> 00:37:23,300
This is what my father gave me.

720
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:24,820
Could he have put some poison in there

721
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:25,780
