722
00:37:26,540 --> 00:37:28,260
Come on, help me choose.

723
00:37:28,260 --> 00:37:29,100
Which should I eat?

724
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:30,580
So many medicines.

725
00:37:30,580 --> 00:37:31,620
Which one should I choose?

726
00:37:31,620 --> 00:37:33,700
Just pick the one with a nice name.

727
00:37:37,060 --> 00:37:38,540
Spring Pill.

728
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:40,340
Spring all year round.

729
00:37:40,780 --> 00:37:41,940
This name is good.

730
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:45,140
This bottle.

731
00:37:45,300 --> 00:37:46,300
This bottle is called

732
00:37:47,260 --> 00:37:48,340
Lotus Powder.

733
00:37:48,820 --> 00:37:50,940
Fragrance from a pool of lotus flowers.

734
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:52,300
This is nice.

735
00:37:53,900 --> 00:37:54,990
This bottle is called Life Pill.

736
00:37:54,990 --> 00:37:55,980
You will use it sooner or later.

737
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:56,860
It should be commonly used.

738
00:38:00,380 --> 00:38:01,540
Take another look.

739
00:38:01,540 --> 00:38:03,420
Is there any word in front?

740
00:38:03,420 --> 00:38:04,260
I'll take another look.

741
00:38:04,660 --> 00:38:05,780
There really is.

742
00:38:06,820 --> 00:38:08,660
Life and Death Pill.

743
00:38:10,220 --> 00:38:11,700
His Royal Highness really

744
00:38:11,700 --> 00:38:13,100
has put everything in here.

745
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:13,940
Right.

